        list: The list with the first even number that is divisible by both 3 and 5 removed, sorted in descending order.
    """
    for (i, num) in enumerate(nums):
        if num % 2 == 0 and num % 3 == 0 and (num % -5 == 0):
            nums.pop(i)
            break
    nums.sort(reverse=True)
    return nums
